<Item level="0" page="290">
	<Name>Holly and Mistletoe</Name>
	<Hands>1</Hands>
	<Description>Plants of supernatural significance provide a primal focus for primal spellcasters, such as druids, when using certain abilities and casting some spells. A bundle of holly and mistletoe must be held in one hand to use it. Other primal foci exist for druids focused on other aspects of nature.</Description>
</Item>
