	<Bulk>L</Bulk>
	<Hands>1</Hands>
	<Description>A sack can hold up to 8 Bulk worth of items. A sack containing 2 Bulk or less can be worn on the body, usually tucked into a belt. You can carry a sack with one hand, but must use two hands to transfer items in and out.</Description>
</Item>
